==Walkthrough==
===Griffin's feather===
{{Map|align=right|mtype=line|width=280|height=340|2891,3454|2889,3447|2884,3445|2882,3444|2881,3442|2879,3430|2876,3429|2873,3432|2871,3446|2875,3454|2874,3459|2872,3469|2869,3475|2867,3481|2864,3483|2864,3485|2865,3490|2867,3499|2867,3508|caption=The path to take to see [[Grimgnash]], the griffin.}}
{{Checklist|
*Talk to [[Sylas]] by the POH portal in Taverley. {{Chat option|5}}
*Talk to [[Grimgnash|Grimgnash the griffin]] on the NE side of [[White Wolf Mountain]] (see map). {{Chat option|1I heard you were a great and mighty Griffin!|1There once was a graveyard filled with undead.|2There lived a skeleton named Skullrot.|4Skullrot was insane!|4Skullrot hungrily grabbed the gnome's hair.|3Started to strangle the poor gnome.|1He saw a hole he could just fit through.}}
*Steal a feather from next to his nest.
*Return to Sylas and give him the feather. {{Chat option|3I should be off, I think.}}
}}

===Rupert's helmet===
{{Checklist|
*Go to the stone tower south of the [[Mind Altar]].
*Climb over the crumbling wall on the East side (58 Thieving)
*Talk-into to the drain pipe. Then talk into it again {{Chat option|2I think I might have an idea!|2I could try and climb up.|2Is there anything up there that can help?}}
*Climb the beard and talk to [[Rupert the Beard]]. (59 Agility)
*Climb down the beard and talk to [[Miazrqa]] behind the tower. {{Chat option|2I see there is an embarrassed-looking dwarf...|4Your second-cousin, twice removed?|4I need a key for the house.|4I should be off, I think.}}
}}

===Miazrqa's pendant===
[[File:Music sheet interface.png|thumb|right|Music sheet]]
{{Needed|[[Leather gloves]] (optional), 2 [[tarromin potion]]s (unf), [[Door key (Witch's House)|door key]] from [[Witch's House (location)|Witch's House]], 3 free inventory spaces}}
'''Note:''' Ensure that your pet is banked or in your inventory as it will prevent you from drinking the shrinking potion
{{Checklist|
*Enter the basement of the [[Witch's House (location)|Witch's House]] next to the POH portal in Taverley.
*Go to the piano on the southern wall, play the notes E-F-E-D-C on the right side (upper), then A-E-G-A on the left side (lower).
*Search the piano.
*Add the [[Shrunk ogleroot]] to your unfinished potions (52 Herblore).
*Go through the south door on {{FloorNumber|uk=0}} and drink a shrinking potion by the mouse hole.
}}

'''Note: '''Level 95 mice will attack you while in this area, hitting up to 9 damage. Protect from Melee prayer is advised if in low armour gear.

'''Warning: Do not exit the area with the level 95 mice until you've collected the pendant.'''

{{Checklist|
*Climb up the nails to the north-east.
*Climb up the nails to the south-west.
*Climb up the nails to the south.
*Climb down the nails to the north-east.
*Climb up the nails to the north-east.
*Take the pendant.
*Travel back to the tower and give the pendant to [[Miazrqa]].
*Talk to [[Rupert]].
*Optional: You can talk to Miazrqa and Rupert again to unlock extra humorous dialogue.
}}

===The beanstalk===
{{Needed|Combat equipment, any [[woodcutting axe]], a [[seed dibber]], a [[watering can]], [[Rupert's helmet]] and a shrink potion.}}
{{Checklist|
*Give Rupert's helmet to [[Sylas]].
*Plant and water the beans in the plot south-west of the Taverley tree patch (45 Farming).
{{Instance}}
*Climb up the beanstalk (59 Agility). You cannot climb with a follower/pet, even if it's in your inventory.
*Defeat [[Glod]] and pick up the [[golden goblin]].
*Talk to Sylas.
*Use a shrinking potion on the beanstalk then chop it down (71 Woodcutting). Be careful not to drink it!
**''If you're stat-boosting make sure you use the shrinking potion before you stat boost - an animation plays and this could cause your stat boost to expire''
*Talk to Sylas.
}}
'''Quest complete!'''

